description:
Minecraft survival. Jarod you spelled "centre" wrong. Nice try Miss Parker, but I'm not going back to that foolishness... Sydney's got my back on this one.


Today we pull the revamp hat trick by fixing up 3 important mechanisms in our world: the flower farm, the super smelter, and gold farm #2 (Goon Farm).
